un-alayhi","tag-chastity-al-husn","tag-humility-al-tawadu","tag-manners-adab","tag-modesty-al-haya","tag-muhammad","tag-parables-amthal","tag-prophetic-virtues-manaqib-nabawi"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-1wZ","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":1758,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/22\/plant-tree-reward-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":5889,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Every tree a Muslim plants is rewarded as charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas bin Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo Muslim plants a tree or sows a seed and then a bird, or a human, or an animal eats from it but that it is charity for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2320, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15362,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/24\/seeing-muhammad-in-your-dreams\/","url_meta":{"origin":5889,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Visions: Seeing the Prophet in your dreams","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever sees me in a dream has truly seen me, for Satan cannot imitate me.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6994, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2266 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":797,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/05\/20\/prophet-business-yahud\/","url_meta":{"origin":5889,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trade: The Prophet has business relations with Jews","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed away while his armor was mortgaged to a Jew for thirty portions of barley. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2916, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1603 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u062a\u064f\u0648\u064f\u0641\u0650\u0651\u064a\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7686,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/prophet-never-says-no-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":5889,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Charity: The Prophet never refused to give in charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was never asked anything for which he said no. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5687, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2311 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0621\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0637\u064f\u0651 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":977,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/08\/05\/prophet-most-generous-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":5889,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: The Prophet was most generous in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was the most generous of people and he was even more generous in Ramadan when Gabriel would meet him. He would meet him every night of Ramadan to study the Quran. Thus, the Prophet would be more\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7561,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/rahmah-to-children-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":5889,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: The Prophet is merciful to children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: A\u00a0bedouin\u00a0came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cYou kiss the children? We do not kiss them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cI cannot put mercy into your heart if Allah has removed it from you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5998, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2317 Grade: Muttafaqun\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5889","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5889"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5889\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5889"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.